# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# HeartsHeal — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# Add these to Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables for production

# ── AI (Required for Haven Companion, AI Journal Prompts, AI Breathing) ──
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# No other environment variables are required.
# HeartsHeal is fully free — no Stripe, no payments.
# All user data is stored locally in the browser (localStorage).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
